      <data key="d8">ACH MORE THAN DOUBLE WITH EXHAUST FANS</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DOSE</data>
      <data key="d10">With both front and rear fans set to exhaust, ACH was more than double the ACH observed when both fans were set to supply.</data>
